  "translations": {
    "en": "Praise be to Allah who gave victory to Muhammad, delighted his eye, and strengthened his support. Shall I not give you glad tidings? I said: Yes, O King. He said: A spy of mine from the land of your people has just come to me and informed me that Allah, Mighty and Majestic, gave victory to His Prophet Muhammad, and destroyed his enemy. Such and such persons were captured, and such and such persons were killed. They met at a place called Badr - as if I am looking at it, for I used to tend sheep there for my master from the Banu Damrah.",
    "ur": "الحمد للہ جس نے محمد کو فتح دی، اس کی آنکھوں کو ٹھنڈا کیا اور اس کی پشت کو مضبوط کیا۔",
    "tr": "Muhammed'e zafer veren, gözünü aydınlatan ve gücünü pekiştiren Allah'a hamd olsun.",
    "fa": "حمد خدایی را که محمد را پیروز کرد و چشمش را روشن ساخت.",
    "id": "Segala puji bagi Allah yang memberikan kemenangan kepada Muhammad, menyejukkan matanya, dan menguatkan dukungannya.",
    "bn": "আল্লাহর প্রশংসা যিনি মুহাম্মাদকে বিজয় দিয়েছেন।",
    "es": "Alabado sea Al-lāh que dio la victoria a Muḥammad.",
    "fr": "Louange à Allāh qui a donné la victoire à Muḥammad.",
    "de": "Alles Lob gebührt Allāh, der Muḥammad den Sieg gab.",
    "ru": "Хвала Аллаху, который дал победу Мухаммаду.",
    "zh": "赞颂安拉，他给了穆罕默德胜利。"
  }
}